    • Satish
      4.0 out of 5 stars Not meant for hard football
      Reviewed in India on 30 August 2024
      Colour: RedVerified Purchase
      The piece appears like school project by children. There is one motor inside with fan. It throws the air outside and makes this piece float on air. The periopheral bumping material is styrofoam (thermocol) fitring tightly by plastic from top. The assembly is good but is not abuse friendly. Some hard kicks and it is likely to stop working. As of now it is working good, all functions works as normal.

      Here is list of features
      - Lightweight battery can be charged by USB type C cable. The charging cable including.
      - Platic top has strong metial quality.
      - Bottom lid is snug fit
      - Styrofoam is even and assembled well
      - Has on On Off button and 3 speed setting button. Both of micro size. You need nail to press it.
      - Default it starts on high power mode. Almost become frictionless on clean flat marble suface. A gentle touch and it keeps moving. Makes loud sound.
      - Medium speed has enough air flow to keep floating but stops after going some distance. Fully usable.
      - Slow speed is terribly slow. Only muted sound and no float. Useless.
      - Play it like big carrom and your kid will be happy. You can't play it like football. My 12 year son demanded it and after playing for 30 mins got bored. He plays real football daily.
